name: Holo-Lights: Love
description: UHD 4K mp4 (2160x3840) for mapping proyector, by Tono C @toocabanelas. Holo-Lights is a series of analog experiments that mix captured light in real time with the interaction of sound. This piece is shot with an ultra HD (6k) cinema camera, a super bright telephoto lens (0.95 f) and a high frame rate per second (160 fps). The image, colors and shapes are 100% generative and not digital.
